OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FA mum from Bristol who has two
OL,8,Fchildren with special educational
OL,9,Fneeds says she worries for their
OL,10,Ffuture as a new poll warns
OL,11,Fprofessionals do not believe SEND
OL,12,Fchildren will be safe if proposed
OL,13,Fgovernments reforms go ahead.
OL,15,FA new poll from the National Autistic
OL,16,FSociety, shared exclusively with ITV
OL,17,FNews, shows 88% of the professionals
OL,18,Fsurveyed worry about support for SEND
OL,19,Fchildren's mental health and wellbeing
OL,20,Fbecause of a lack of capacity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
