PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FIt also found 79% of autistic people
OL,8,Fand their carers do not trust that
OL,9,Fproposed reforms will improve
OL,10,Fexperiences for children with SEND and
OL,11,Ftheir families.
OL,13,FEarlier this year the government set
OL,14,Fout a proposed Schools White Paper - a
OL,15,Fraft of reforms to the SEND system in
OL,16,FEngland in an attempt to make it more
OL,17,Finclusive, shifting from a model that
OL,18,Fhas seen a growing number of young
OL,19,Fpeople attend specialist schools.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
