FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FIt laid out plans for mainstream
OL,8,Fschools to receive direct funding
OL,9,Fincluding investment in training for
OL,10,Fadaptive teaching styles and money to
OL,11,Ffund specialists such as SEND teachers
OL,12,Fand speech and language therapists.
OL,14,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,15,Fpromised that education, health and
OL,16,Fcare plans (EHCPs), a legal document
OL,17,Fsetting out the support children with
OL,18,FSEND are entitled to, will stay "for
OL,19,Fchildren with the most complex needs".
OL,26,@zD@aOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FBut the changes mean around one in
OL,8,Feight children with SEND who currently
OL,9,Fhave the highest support will
OL,10,Ftransition to new plans between 2030
OL,11,Fand 2035.
OL,13,FMother of two, Gill Crea, from
OL,14,FBristol, said she and many other
OL,15,Fparents of SEND children don't feel as
OL,16,Fthough the government have looked at
OL,17,Fthe system to properly understand what
OL,18,Fneeds to change.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"We are one of the lucky ones, we got
OL,8,Four EHCP, our children get the support
OL,9,Fthey need, many families haven't had
OL,10,Fthat which is really difficult.
OL,12,F"It's not about treating every child
OL,13,Fequally it's being equitable... A SEND
OL,14,Fchild may need a smaller class size,
OL,15,Fthey may need specialist equipment,
OL,16,Fthey may need further help, which
OL,17,Fisn't always accessible when you're in
OL,18,Fa mainstream location.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"The amount of funding that the
OL,8,Fgovernment is offering is not going to
OL,9,Fspread across all those schools to
OL,10,Fgive the inclusion they are suggesting
OL,11,Fis going to be able.
OL,13,F"The fact they are taking legal rights
OL,14,Faway from children to be able to
OL,15,Fassess this is something that makes
OL,16,Fmany parents worry that their child
OL,17,Fisn't going to be treated in a
OL,18,Fequitable way."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FMel Merritt, National Autistic Society
OL,8,Fdescribed the data from the National
OL,9,FAutistic Society poll as concerning.
OL,11,F"Two thirds of teachers have said they
OL,12,Fare worried about keeping SEND
OL,13,Fchildren safe in their classroom
OL,14,Fbecause of a lack of capacity.
OL,16,F"It shows how broken the SEND system
OL,17,Fis that that many teachers have that
OL,18,Fconcern about safety.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"Only 1 in 10 parents feel like their
OL,8,Fchildren with SEND needs are safe at
OL,9,Fschool.
OL,11,F"Its a concern for anyone who's close
OL,12,Fto the system can see this and the
OL,13,Fgovernment have to get these reforms
OL,14,Fright."
OL,16,FShe went on to explain how the reform
OL,17,Fneeds to be a 'whole school approach'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779199898
OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,F"The government's current plans are
OL,8,Fambitious but even with the funding
OL,9,Fthat they have already put in it's not
OL,10,Fenough," she said.
OL,12,F"A lot of the reforms rely on teachers
OL,13,Fbeing better trained, more resource
OL,14,Fand more time but no extra teaching
OL,15,Fcapacity have really been put into the
OL,16,Fsystem."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
