OL,3,C'Worried for their future': New poll
OL,4,Cfinds fears around SEND children's
OL,5,Csafety
OL,7,FThe government hopes the #4 billion
OL,8,Fpackage will help make mainstream
OL,9,Fschools more inclusive, including a
OL,10,F#1.6 billion 'inclusive mainstream
OL,11,Ffund' for early years, schools and
OL,12,Fcolleges, and #1.8 billion to place
OL,13,Fspecialist staff such as SEND teachers
OL,14,Fand speech therapists in every area.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
